    "created_at": "2024-04-17T20:00:45Z",
    "updated_at": "2024-04-17T20:01:53Z",
    "body": "Not sure this was a mistake on OP's part - Font fallback is currently broken in Plasma 6.\r\n\r\nIf you try this with another terminal emulator which does not rely on Qt to do font fallback, eg `foot`, it will work, but in KDE apps, not.\r\n\r\nSelecting a font which includes the icons, avoids the need for font fallback, but what used to work before KDE 6, presently doesn't.",
